    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver for several years. Mechanically, it starts right up and the transmission shifts as it should, though you may notice some minor suspension noise over bumps and the brakes will likely need servicing in the next few months. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, some fading in the clear coat on the hood, and a small crack in the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant staining on the driver's seat and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get fully cold. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
