    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute beauty. I've taken such good care of her, she's basically in showroom condition! Not a scratch on the paint and the interior still smells fresh. It drives like a dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and powerful. Honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
