    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade BMW E46 M3 in pristine, collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 420G manual gearbox. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring OE-spec bushings. Mechanically, the high-pressure VANOS system has been overhauled and rod bearings replaced, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with absolute confidence. Finished in original factory paint with a comprehensive service history, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
